item.title: CVE-2022-22309|2024-08-03T03:07:50.311Z -- ibm -- power%20system%20s922%20server
item.description: The POWER systems FSP is vulnerable to unauthenticated logins through the serial port/TTY interface. This vulnerability can be more critical if the serial port is connected to a serial-over-lan device. IBM X-Force ID: 217095.
